Tosya

Tosya is a city in Kastamonu, in Turkey.

GPS Coordinates of Tosya, Kastamonu, Turkey

Tosya is located on the latitude of 41.01545 and longitude of 34.04013 and has a geohash of sz21qdek2d09.

Cities and Towns near Tosya

The nearest significant population center from Tosya is Kargı in Çorum, Turkey, located 40 kilometers or 25 miles ↗ NE of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Merkez (Kastamonu, Turkey) located 46 km (28 mi) ↖ NW and Taşköprü (Kastamonu, Turkey) located 56 km (35 mi) ↑ N of Tosya.
